msgid "What is your return policy?"
msgstr ""

msgid "We offer a 30-day satisfaction guarantee. If you're not completely satisfied with your purchase, return the product for a full refund. Simply contact our support team to initiate the return process."
msgstr ""

msgid "How long does shipping take?"
msgstr ""

msgid "Standard shipping takes 3-5 business days within the continental US. Express shipping (1-2 days) is available at checkout. International shipping typically takes 7-14 business days depending on the destination."
msgstr ""

msgid "Are your products vegan and cruelty-free?"
msgstr ""

msgid "Yes! All Dragon Glow products are 100% vegan and cruelty-free. We never test on animals and only use ingredients that align with our ethical values."
msgstr ""

msgid "Can I use multiple products together?"
msgstr ""

msgid "Absolutely! Our products are designed to work synergistically. We recommend starting with a cleanser, followed by serum, then moisturizer. Check individual product pages for specific layering instructions."
msgstr ""

